*.log
.cache/

# ─── Result artifacts (regenerated each run, keep out of git) ──
result/

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The following are intentionally tracked so the app's
# uploaded/generated assets can be versioned:
#   - data/<game>/frames   -> uploaded game screenshots
#   - data/<game>/labels   -> uploaded ground-truth labels
#   - universal_noise/     -> trained universal_noise.pt files
#   - pretrained_models/custom -> uploaded custom .pt models
# Nothing below this line is ignored.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
!data/
!data/**
!universal_noise/
!universal_noise/**
!pretrained_models/
!pretrained_models/**
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg
!*.png
!*.bmp
!*.pt